#-----Menus
Mod4 space :rootmenu
OnTitlebar Mouse3 :windowmenu
OnDesktop Mouse3 :rootmenu
OnDesktop Mouse1 :HideMenus

#-----Shortcuts
Mod4 Shift e :Exit
Mod4 Enter :Exec fbrun
Control Mod1 t :Exec urxvt -bg black -fg cyan
Mod1 Tab :NextWindow
Mod1 Tab Shift :PrevWindow

#-----Window position
##----Full
Mod4 Left :MacroCmd {Raise} {Focus} {MoveTo 0 0 TopLeft} {ResizeTo 50% 100%}
Mod4 Right :MacroCmd {Raise} {Focus} {MoveTo 0 0 TopRight} {ResizeTo 50% 100%}
Mod4 Up :Maximize
Mod4 Down :Close
##----Partial
Mod4 Shift Up :MacroCmd {Raise} {Focus} {MoveTo 0 0 TopLeft} {ResizeTo 50% 50%}
Mod4 Shift Right :MacroCmd {Raise} {Focus} {MoveTo 0 0 TopRight} {ResizeTo 50% 50%}
Mod4 Shift Down :MacroCmd {Raise} {Focus} {MoveTo 0 0 BottomRight} {ResizeTo 50% 50%}
Mod4 Shift Left :MacroCmd {Raise} {Focus} {MoveTo 0 0 BottomLeft} {ResizeTo 50% 50%}

#-----Workspaces
Mod4 1 :Workspace 1
Mod4 2 :Workspace 2
Mod4 3 :Workspace 3
Mod4 4 :Workspace 4
##--Cycle
Control Mod1 Right :TakeToNextWorkspace
Control Mod1 Left :TakeToPrevWorkspace
OnDesktop Mouse5 :NextWorkspace
OnDesktop Mouse4 :PrevWorkspace
##--Window
Mod4 Shift 1 :TakeToWorkspace 1
Mod4 Shift 2 :TakeToWorkspace 2
Mod4 Shift 3 :TakeToWorkspace 3
Mod4 Shift 4 :TakeToWorkspace 4
